Consider the following two code segments. Code segment 2 is a revision of code segment 1 in which the loop header has been changed.

Code Segment 1for (int k = 1; k <= 5; k++) 
{ 
 System.out.print(k); 
} 

Code Segment 2for (int k = 5; k >= 1; k--) 
{ 
 System.out.print(k); 
}
